:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:40:\"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/content/\";a:1:{s:7:\"encoded\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:4748:\"<p>We&#8217;re thrilled to announce the latest addition to our website — <strong>Trends</strong>!</p>\n\n\n\n<p>This new page is your go-to resource for learning the strategies behind websites with explosive organic growth.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>We&#8217;ll share their winning techniques so that YOU can boost traffic and rankings on YOUR site.</p>\n\n\n\n<p><strong>SEO case studies </strong>are at the heart of this exciting addition, offering real-world examples <em>and</em> actionable insights.</p>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Why SEO Case Studies?</h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Many website owners struggle to climb the search engine results page (SERP) and get the traffic that comes with higher rankings.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>You look at the competition and wonder: What are they doing so differently to come out on top? And how can I get the same results for my website?</p>\n\n\n\n<p>That&#8217;s where our SEO case studies come into play.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>SEO case studies allow us to <strong>uncover the precise strategies</strong> fueling a website&#8217;s organic growth.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Then, <strong>we share these findings with</strong> <strong>you</strong>.</p>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">What You’ll Discover</h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Our <strong>Trends</strong> page is your backstage pass to SEO strategies that unlock your website&#8217;s organic performance.</p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><a href=\"https://aioseo.com/trends/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"778\" height=\"700\" src=\"https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/AIOSEO-Trends-SEO-Case-Studies.jpg\" alt=\"Screenshot of the AIOSEO Trends page, which uses SEO case studies to teach website owners how to leverage winning SEO strategies.\" class=\"wp-image-244486\" title=\"AIOSEO Trends\" srcset=\"https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/AIOSEO-Trends-SEO-Case-Studies.jpg 778w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/AIOSEO-Trends-SEO-Case-Studies-300x270.jpg 300w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/AIOSEO-Trends-SEO-Case-Studies-768x691.jpg 768w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/AIOSEO-Trends-SEO-Case-Studies-600x540.jpg 600w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/AIOSEO-Trends-SEO-Case-Studies-67x60.jpg 67w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/AIOSEO-Trends-SEO-Case-Studies-100x90.jpg 100w\" sizes=\"100vw\" /></a></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>Here&#8217;s what you can expect in each SEO case study:</p>\n\n\n\n<ol>\n<li><strong>Success Stories:</strong> We&#8217;ll take you behind the scenes of websites that have achieved outstanding organic traffic growth. From niche blogs to eCommerce giants, these case studies span an array of industries, providing valuable insights for all.</li>\n\n\n\n<li><strong>Traffic Strategies:</strong> We won&#8217;t just showcase success; we&#8217;ll decode the strategies that powered it. You&#8217;ll gain a clear understanding of the tactics and techniques these websites employed to make it to the top of the SERP.</li>\n\n\n\n<li><strong>Replication Guides:</strong> It&#8217;s not enough to know <em>what</em> others did. Our SEO case studies will guide you on <em>how to implement these strategies on your website</em>. You&#8217;ll receive step-by-step instructions to kickstart your own journey toward greater organic traffic.</li>\n\n\n\n<li><strong>Why These Strategies Matter:</strong> Understanding the <em>why</em> is just as important as the <em>how</em>. We&#8217;ll share insights into why these strategies work so you&#8217;re empowered to use their potential on your website.</li>\n\n\n\n<li><strong>Tools of the Trade:</strong> Success often hinges on having the right tools. We&#8217;ll recommend the tools and resources you need to implement the strategies effectively on your WordPress site.</li>\n</ol>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Trends: Helping YOU Win by Learning From the Best</h2>\n\n\n\n<p>At All in One SEO, we&#8217;re dedicated to helping you achieve online success.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Our new <strong>Trends</strong> page lifts the veil on SEO and shares the growth strategies that actually make a difference.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>We hope these SEO case studies serve as <em>your</em> playbook to <strong>boost your website’s rankings</strong> and <strong>drive more organic traffic</strong>.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>So, what are you waiting for?</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Hop on over to <strong><a href=\"https://aioseo.com/trends/\" title=\"\">Trends</a></strong>, and let us know what you think!</p>\n\n\n\n<p>We think you&#8217;re going to like it there.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>– Benjamin Rojas<br>President, All in One SEO</p>The post <a href=\"https://aioseo.com/announcing-trends-seo-case-studies-that-boost-your-traffic/\">Announcing Trends: SEO Case Studies That Boost YOUR Traffic</a> first appeared on <a href=\"https://aioseo.com\">AIOSEO</a>.\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:36:\"http://wellformedweb.org/CommentAPI/\";a:1:{s:10:\"commentRss\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:83:\"https://aioseo.com/announcing-trends-seo-case-studies-that-boost-your-traffic/feed/\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:38:\"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/slash/\";a:1:{s:8:\"comments\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:1:\"0\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}}}i:2;a:6:{s:4:\"data\";s:88:\"\n		\n		\n					\n		\n		\n		\n				\n		\n		\n		\n		\n		\n		\n\n					\n										\n					\n					\n			\n		\n		\n			\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";s:5:\"child\";a:5:{s:0:\"\";a:7:{s:5:\"title\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:54:\"Sponsored Links: What are They and Do They Impact SEO?\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:4:\"link\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:168:\"https://aioseo.com/sponsored-links-what-are-they-and-do-they-impact-seo/?utm_source=rss&utm_medium=rss&utm_campaign=sponsored-links-what-are-they-and-do-they-impact-seo\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:8:\"comments\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:80:\"https://aioseo.com/sponsored-links-what-are-they-and-do-they-impact-seo/#respond\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:7:\"pubDate\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:31:\"Tue, 07 Nov 2023 14:00:00 +0000\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:8:\"category\";a:6:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:4:\"Blog\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}i:1;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:8:\"SEO Tips\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}i:2;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:39:\"How to add sponsored links in WordPress\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}i:3;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:15:\"Link attributes\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}i:4;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:20:\"What are paid links?\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}i:5;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:25:\"What are sponosred links?\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:4:\"guid\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:28:\"https://aioseo.com/?p=244508\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:1:{s:0:\"\";a:1:{s:11:\"isPermaLink\";s:5:\"false\";}}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:11:\"description\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:491:\"<p>If you&#8217;ve ventured into Search Engine Optimization (SEO), you&#8217;ve likely come across the term &#8220;sponsored links.&#8221; Usually, this refers to the practice of paying another site to link to yours, a strategy some businesses use to try and boost their&#8230;</p>\nThe post <a href=\"https://aioseo.com/sponsored-links-what-are-they-and-do-they-impact-seo/\">Sponsored Links: What are They and Do They Impact SEO?</a> first appeared on <a href=\"https://aioseo.com\">AIOSEO</a>.\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:32:\"http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/\";a:1:{s:7:\"creator\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:15:\"Sherrie Gossett\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:40:\"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/content/\";a:1:{s:7:\"encoded\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:33486:\"<p>If you&#8217;ve ventured into Search Engine Optimization (SEO), you&#8217;ve likely come across the term &#8220;sponsored links.&#8221;</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Usually, this refers to the practice of paying another site to link to yours, a strategy some businesses use to try and boost their online visibility. However, it&#8217;s essential to understand that search engine algorithms don’t give all links equal weight.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>As we delve deeper into the topic, we&#8217;ll explore what sponsored links are, the role they play, and how, if mishandled, they can harm your SEO.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Learning about sponsored links will equip you to make better link-building decisions.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Before we begin, let&#8217;s look at why marketers prize backlinks (links from other sites to yours).</p>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-group aioseo-table-of-contents has-theme-info-background-color has-background is-layout-flow wp-block-group-is-layout-flow\"><div class=\"wp-block-group__inner-container\">\n<p>In This Article</p>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-aioseo-table-of-contents\"><ul><li><a href=\"#aioseo-backlinks-and-seo\">Backlinks and SEO</a></li><li><a href=\"#aioseo-what-are-sponsored-links\">What are Sponsored Links?</a></li><li><a href=\"#aioseo-how-do-you-tell-if-a-link-is-sponsored\">How Can You Tell if a Link is Sponsored?</a></li><li><a href=\"#aioseo-understanding-link-attributes\">Understanding Link Attributes</a><ul><li><a href=\"#aioseo-exceptions-to-using-the-sponsored-tag\">Exceptions to Using the Sponsored Tag</a></li></ul></li><li><a href=\"#aioseo-dofollow-links-the-crown-jewel-in-link-building\">Dofollow Links: the Crown Jewel in Link Building</a><ul></ul></li><li><a href=\"#aioseo-how-does-this-apply-to-link-building-and-seo\">How Does This Apply to Link Building and SEO?</a></li><li><a href=\"#aioseo-how-to-attract-backlinks-with-seo\">How to Attract Backlinks With SEO</a><ul><li><a href=\"#aioseo-1-optimize-your-pages-for-seo\">1. Optimize Your Pages for SEO</a><ul></ul></li><li><a href=\"#aioseo-2-choose-keywords-that-are-easy-to-rank-for\">2. Choose Keywords That are Easy to Rank For</a></li></ul></li><li><a href=\"#aioseo-how-to-create-sponsored-links-using-aioseo\">How to Create Sponsored Links Using AIOSEO</a><ul></ul></li></ul></div>\n</div></div>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\" id=\"aioseo-backlinks-and-seo\">Backlinks and SEO</h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Backlinks are a crucial search engine ranking factor. Interestingly, they can impact your site positively or negatively.</p>\n\n\n\n<ul>\n<li>Links from <em>trusted</em> sites can boost your rankings.</li>\n\n\n\n<li>But links from <em>spammy</em> sites can lower your rankings.</li>\n\n\n\n<li>Some links will predictably have <em>no impact</em> on your SEO.</li>\n</ul>\n\n\n\n<p>Why is this?</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Google sees backlinks from reputable sites to yours as an endorsement of your content. These<em> </em><a href=\"https://aioseo.com/referring-domains-vs-backlinks-seo/\">inbound links</a> can significantly boost rankings and revenue.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>However, if you intentionally acquire links from spammy or fraudulent sites, Google will view this as a <a href=\"https://developers.google.com/search/docs/essentials/spam-policies\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener nofollow\" title=\"\">link scheme</a>. And that can trigger search engine penalties.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Lastly, sponsored links have <em>no impact</em> on SEO. That&#8217;s not surprising since anyone can acquire these links. And sponsored links aren&#8217;t endorsements.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Now, let&#8217;s take a closer look at sponsored links.</p>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\" id=\"aioseo-what-are-sponsored-links\">What are Sponsored Links?</h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Sponsored links are paid links. A sponsored link is acquired by paying another website to link to yours.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>These links are sold in different ways.</p>\n\n\n\n<ul>\n<li><strong>Link insertion</strong>: The buyer pays for a link to be inserted somewhere on the seller&#8217;s site.</li>\n\n\n\n<li><strong>Guest post</strong>: the buyer pays for content (sometimes called an advertorial) to be published with the agreement that the page includes a backlink to the buyer&#8217;s site.</li>\n</ul>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\" id=\"aioseo-how-do-you-tell-if-a-link-is-sponsored\">How Can You Tell if a Link is Sponsored?</h2>\n\n\n\n<p>You can tell if a link is sponsored by <a href=\"https://aioseo.com/how-to-view-page-source/\" title=\"\">viewing the code</a> for the link. This code, called a link attribute, tells Google the relationship between the linking site and the linked page.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>The code for the sponsored link attribute is rel=&#8221;sponsored&#8221;. Here, &#8220;rel&#8221; stands for relationship. And &#8220;sponsored&#8221; is the &#8220;value&#8221; of the attribute.</p>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\" id=\"aioseo-understanding-link-attributes\">Understanding Link Attributes</h2>\n\n\n\n<p>As you may have guessed, the sponsored attribute isn’t the only one that can be added to links.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Here&#8217;s a table listing the 3 link attributes most important in digital marketing.</p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-table\"><table><tbody><tr><td><strong>Link Attribute</strong></td><td><strong>Description</strong></td><td><strong>SEO value</strong></td><td><strong>How it appears in code</strong></td></tr><tr><td><em>Sponsored</em> attribute</td><td>This attribute is used to identify links that are advertisements or paid placements. Google doesn&#8217;t count them for ranking purposes.</td><td>None</td><td>rel=&#8221;sponsored&#8221;</td></tr><tr><td><em>Nofollow</em> attribute</td><td>Tells search engines not to follow a specific link. This link type doesn&#8217;t pass any authority to the linked page.</td><td>None</td><td>rel=&#8221;nofollow&#8221;</td></tr><tr><td><em>UGC</em> attribute</td><td>Stands for User-Generated Content. It&#8217;s used for links within user-generated content, like forum posts and comments.</td><td>None, possibly negative*</td><td>rel=&#8221;ugc&#8221;</td></tr></tbody></table><figcaption class=\"wp-element-caption\"><em>* Sites that allow logged-in users to create articles typically wind up with mediocre content. This can result in Google choosing to deprioritize crawling the site (or a section of the site) and it can </em><a href=\"https://www.searchenginejournal.com/google-confirms-quality-is-foremost-factor-in-search-indexing/496666/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\"><em>prevent indexing</em></a><em>.</em> </figcaption></figure>\n\n\n\n<p><strong>Takeaways:</strong></p>\n\n\n\n<ul>\n<li>Marking paid links as &#8220;sponsored&#8221; is a <a href=\"https://developers.google.com/search/docs/crawling-indexing/qualify-outbound-links\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener nofollow\" title=\"\">best practice</a>.</li>\n\n\n\n<li>Buying or selling links to manipulate rankings is <a href=\"https://developers.google.com/search/docs/essentials/spam-policies#link-spam\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener nofollow\" title=\"\">forbidden by Google</a>.</li>\n\n\n\n<li>Hosting poor quality user-generated content can <a href=\"https://developers.google.com/search/updates/helpful-content-update\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener nofollow\" title=\"\">harm your over all site ranking</a>.</li>\n</ul>\n\n\n\n<h3 class=\"wp-block-heading\" id=\"aioseo-exceptions-to-using-the-sponsored-tag\">Exceptions to Using the Sponsored Tag</h3>\n\n\n\n<p>Large publishers like Bloomberg sell multimedia packages promoting advertisers. These sponsored pages are marked as such.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>For example, see <a href=\"https://sponsored.bloomberg.com/immersive/hyundai/the-h2-economy\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener nofollow\" title=\"\">this page</a> about hydrogen power and Hyundai&#8217;s investment in it.</p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"1024\" height=\"385\" src=\"https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/bloomberg-sponsored-content-example-1024x385.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-244549\" srcset=\"https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/bloomberg-sponsored-content-example-1024x385.jpg 1024w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/bloomberg-sponsored-content-example-300x113.jpg 300w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/bloomberg-sponsored-content-example-768x289.jpg 768w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/bloomberg-sponsored-content-example-1536x578.jpg 1536w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/bloomberg-sponsored-content-example-2048x771.jpg 2048w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/bloomberg-sponsored-content-example-600x226.jpg 600w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/bloomberg-sponsored-content-example-159x60.jpg 159w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/bloomberg-sponsored-content-example-239x90.jpg 239w\" sizes=\"100vw\" /></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>While the few links on the page to Hyundai don&#8217;t carry the sponsored tag, the page is clearly marked as sponsored content.</p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large is-resized\"><img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/bloomberg-sponsored-content-label-1024x366.png\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-244550\" style=\"width:454px;height:162px\" width=\"454\" height=\"162\" srcset=\"https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/bloomberg-sponsored-content-label-1024x366.png 1024w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/bloomberg-sponsored-content-label-300x107.png 300w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/bloomberg-sponsored-content-label-768x274.png 768w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/bloomberg-sponsored-content-label-600x214.png 600w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/bloomberg-sponsored-content-label-168x60.png 168w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/bloomberg-sponsored-content-label-252x90.png 252w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/bloomberg-sponsored-content-label.png 1279w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 454px) 100vw, 454px\" /></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>Additionally, the page is published on a subdomain, &#8220;<strong>sponsored</strong>.bloomberg.com.&#8221;</p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large is-resized\"><img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/sponsored-content-url-example-1-1024x109.png\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-244555\" style=\"width:611px;height:65px\" width=\"611\" height=\"65\" srcset=\"https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/sponsored-content-url-example-1-1024x109.png 1024w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/sponsored-content-url-example-1-300x32.png 300w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/sponsored-content-url-example-1-768x82.png 768w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/sponsored-content-url-example-1-600x64.png 600w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/sponsored-content-url-example-1-190x20.png 190w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/sponsored-content-url-example-1-750x80.png 750w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/sponsored-content-url-example-1.png 1145w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 611px) 100vw, 611px\" /></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>It&#8217;s worth noting that the purpose of this sponsored page is to communicate with Bloomberg subscribers, not to drive a rankings boost via inbound links. (There are only 2 Hyundai links on the page.)</p>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\" id=\"aioseo-dofollow-links-the-crown-jewel-in-link-building\">Dofollow Links: the Crown Jewel in Link Building</h2>\n\n\n\n<p>So far, we&#8217;ve learned that sponsored, nofollow, or UGC links <em>don&#8217;t</em> confer SEO value. And we know that links from quality websites can significantly impact SEO.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>For these good links to influence ranking, they must be &#8220;dofollow&#8221; links.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>&#8220;Dofollow&#8221; sounds like an odd term. It just means a <em>regular</em> hyperlink, i.e., one that doesn&#8217;t have the link attributes we mentioned.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Let&#8217;s look at a <em>dofollow</em> link in HTML code, followed by links with the 3 previously discussed attributes.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>For anchor text, we&#8217;ll use the phrase &#8220;Example Site.&#8221;</p>\n\n\n\n<p><strong>Dofollow link</strong>:</p>\n\n\n\n<pre class=\"wp-block-code\"><code>&lt;a href=\"https://example.com\"&gt;Example Site&lt;/a&gt;</code></pre>\n\n\n\n<p><strong>Sponsored link:</strong></p>\n\n\n\n<pre class=\"wp-block-code\"><code>&lt;a href=\"https://example.com\" rel=\"sponsored\">Example Site&lt;/a></code></pre>\n\n\n\n<p><strong>Nofollow link</strong>:</p>\n\n\n\n<pre class=\"wp-block-code\"><code>&lt;a href=\"https://example.com\" rel=\"nofollow\"&gt;Example Site&lt;/a&gt;</code></pre>\n\n\n\n<p><strong>UGC link</strong>:</p>\n\n\n\n<pre class=\"wp-block-code\"><code>&lt;a href=\"https://example.com\" rel=\"ugc\"&gt;Example Site&lt;/a&gt;</code></pre>\n\n\n\n<h3 class=\"wp-block-heading\" id=\"aioseo-links-can-carry-multiple-attributes\">Links Can Carry Multiple Attributes</h3>\n\n\n\n<p>Those learning HTML may be interested to know that links can carry <em>multiple</em> attributes.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Here are some examples.</p>\n\n\n\n<p><strong>Sponsored link with nofollow attribute</strong>:</p>\n\n\n\n<pre class=\"wp-block-code\"><code>&lt;a href=\"https://example.com\" rel=\"sponsored nofollow\">Example Site&lt;/a></code></pre>\n\n\n\n<p><strong>UGC link with nofollow attribute</strong>:</p>\n\n\n\n<pre class=\"wp-block-code\"><code>&lt;a href=\"https://example.com\" rel=\"ugc nofollow\">Example Site&lt;/a></code></pre>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\" id=\"aioseo-how-does-this-apply-to-link-building-and-seo\">How Does This Apply to Link Building and SEO?</h2>\n\n\n\n<p>While sponsored links don’t boost SEO, they can increase traffic and raise brand awareness.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>If you’re considering this option, choose a website that attracts the same target audience as yours. Otherwise, the traffic may be of little value.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Additionally, realize that you’ll rely on the honesty of the site selling sponsored links when they provide data about their traffic numbers.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>And skip contributing articles to UGC (user-generated content) websites. The content on these sites is typically mediocre. Exceptions are sites like <a href=\"https://tabbforum.com/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener nofollow\" title=\"\">TabbFORUM</a> that publish content from accomplished individuals and experts.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Lastly, use SEO to <strong><em>attract</em> backlinks</strong>.</p>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\" id=\"aioseo-how-to-attract-backlinks-with-seo\">How to Attract Backlinks With SEO</h2>\n\n\n\n<p>If you publish high-quality content that offers unique value, it<em> will</em> attract backlinks.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>And these backlinks create a positive cycle. As people link to your content, it ranks higher. Then, more people discover it and link to it, too.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Consistency in publishing high-quality content and attracting links can lead to a hockey-stick growth pattern.</p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large is-resized\"><a href=\"https://aioseo.com/referring-domains-vs-backlinks-seo/\"><img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/bringatrailer-referring-domains-1024x392.png\" alt=\"referring domains chart\" class=\"wp-image-244558\" style=\"width:706px;height:270px\" width=\"706\" height=\"270\" srcset=\"https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/bringatrailer-referring-domains-1024x392.png 1024w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/bringatrailer-referring-domains-300x115.png 300w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/bringatrailer-referring-domains-768x294.png 768w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/bringatrailer-referring-domains-1536x588.png 1536w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/bringatrailer-referring-domains-2048x784.png 2048w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/bringatrailer-referring-domains-600x230.png 600w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/bringatrailer-referring-domains-157x60.png 157w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/bringatrailer-referring-domains-235x90.png 235w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 706px) 100vw, 706px\" /></a><figcaption class=\"wp-element-caption\"><em>Ahrefs chart of BringATrailer.com’s <a href=\"https://aioseo.com/referring-domains-vs-backlinks-seo/\">referring domains growth</a> from 2014 on.</em></figcaption></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>A key part of publishing quality content is optimizing it for SEO.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>WordPress site owners can use a plugin to simplify this process.</p>\n\n\n\n<h3 class=\"wp-block-heading\" id=\"aioseo-1-optimize-your-pages-for-seo\">1. Optimize Your Pages for SEO</h3>\n\n\n\n<p>We recommend using All in One SEO (AIOSEO), a WordPress plugin that automates many tasks.</p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"1024\" height=\"485\" src=\"https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/12/aioseo-homepage-1024x485.png\" alt=\"aioseo homepage\" class=\"wp-image-140989\" srcset=\"https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/12/aioseo-homepage-1024x485.png 1024w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/12/aioseo-homepage-300x142.png 300w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/12/aioseo-homepage-768x364.png 768w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/12/aioseo-homepage-600x284.png 600w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/12/aioseo-homepage-127x60.png 127w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/12/aioseo-homepage-190x90.png 190w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/12/aioseo-homepage.png 1260w\" sizes=\"100vw\" /></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>Designed to be easy for beginners to use, All in One SEO analyzes your web pages and provides specific action steps to improve them.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>In this way, the plugin takes a lot of the guesswork out of SEO.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>All in One SEO (AIOSEO) is an established plugin with thousands of 5-star reviews on WordPress.org.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>After <a href=\"https://aioseo.com/pricing/\">downloading</a> and <a href=\"https://aioseo.com/docs/installing-addons-for-all-in-one-seo-pro/\">installing</a> the plugin, AIOSEO will begin analyzing your site.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>While logged into WordPress, you’ll see the AIOSEO sidebar to the right.</p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large is-resized\"><img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/aioseo-sidebar-735x1024.png\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-244561\" style=\"width:389px;height:542px\" width=\"389\" height=\"542\" srcset=\"https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/aioseo-sidebar-735x1024.png 735w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/aioseo-sidebar-215x300.png 215w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/aioseo-sidebar-768x1070.png 768w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/aioseo-sidebar-600x836.png 600w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/aioseo-sidebar-43x60.png 43w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/aioseo-sidebar-65x90.png 65w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/aioseo-sidebar.png 798w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 389px) 100vw, 389px\" /></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>This is where you’ll find the plugin’s analysis and recommendations.</p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large is-resized\"><img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/aioseo-focus-keyphrase-not-in-title-1024x237.png\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-244563\" style=\"width:398px;height:92px\" width=\"398\" height=\"92\" srcset=\"https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/aioseo-focus-keyphrase-not-in-title-1024x237.png 1024w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/aioseo-focus-keyphrase-not-in-title-300x70.png 300w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/aioseo-focus-keyphrase-not-in-title-768x178.png 768w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/aioseo-focus-keyphrase-not-in-title-600x139.png 600w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/aioseo-focus-keyphrase-not-in-title-190x44.png 190w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/aioseo-focus-keyphrase-not-in-title-388x90.png 388w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/aioseo-focus-keyphrase-not-in-title.png 1105w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 398px) 100vw, 398px\" /></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>The plugin will also analyze your page’s readability. This means how easy your content is to <em>read </em>and <em>understand</em>.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>And you’ll get formatting recommendations that make screen reading easier for your users.</p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large is-resized\"><img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/aioseo-readability-errors-582x1024.png\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-244564\" style=\"width:390px;height:686px\" width=\"390\" height=\"686\" srcset=\"https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/aioseo-readability-errors-582x1024.png 582w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/aioseo-readability-errors-170x300.png 170w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/aioseo-readability-errors-768x1352.png 768w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/aioseo-readability-errors-600x1056.png 600w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/aioseo-readability-errors-34x60.png 34w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/aioseo-readability-errors-51x90.png 51w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/aioseo-readability-errors.png 790w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 390px) 100vw, 390px\" /></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>Next, you can easily turn your web pages into rich snippets.</p>\n\n\n\n<h4 class=\"wp-block-heading\" id=\"aioseo-turn-your-web-pages-into-rich-snippets\">Turn Your Web Pages into Rich Snippets</h4>\n\n\n\n<p>A <a href=\"https://aioseo.com/how-to-add-rich-snippets-to-wordpress/\">rich snippet</a> is a web page that has special code, called <em>schema markup</em>, added to it.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>This code helps Google understands your page better and rank it for relevant keywords.</p>\n\n\n\n<ul>\n<li>Rich snippets can help your page rank for multiple related keywords.</li>\n\n\n\n<li>And some rich snippets are <em>visually prominent</em>.</li>\n</ul>\n\n\n\n<p>To get an idea of the latter, here’s an example of a standard search snippet.</p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"1024\" height=\"236\" src=\"https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/standard-search-snippet-academy-flannel-shirts-1024x236.png\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-244565\" srcset=\"https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/standard-search-snippet-academy-flannel-shirts-1024x236.png 1024w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/standard-search-snippet-academy-flannel-shirts-300x69.png 300w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/standard-search-snippet-academy-flannel-shirts-768x177.png 768w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/standard-search-snippet-academy-flannel-shirts-1536x354.png 1536w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/standard-search-snippet-academy-flannel-shirts-2048x472.png 2048w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/standard-search-snippet-academy-flannel-shirts-600x138.png 600w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/standard-search-snippet-academy-flannel-shirts-190x44.png 190w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/standard-search-snippet-academy-flannel-shirts-390x90.png 390w\" sizes=\"100vw\" /></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>And here’s a <em>rich snippet</em>.</p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"1024\" height=\"394\" src=\"https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/rich-snippet-example-duluth-trading-1024x394.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-244570\" srcset=\"https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/rich-snippet-example-duluth-trading-1024x394.jpg 1024w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/rich-snippet-example-duluth-trading-300x116.jpg 300w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/rich-snippet-example-duluth-trading-768x296.jpg 768w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/rich-snippet-example-duluth-trading-1536x592.jpg 1536w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/rich-snippet-example-duluth-trading-600x231.jpg 600w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/rich-snippet-example-duluth-trading-156x60.jpg 156w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/rich-snippet-example-duluth-trading-234x90.jpg 234w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/rich-snippet-example-duluth-trading.jpg 1760w\" sizes=\"100vw\" /><figcaption class=\"wp-element-caption\"><em>Above: This rich snippet features 5 links, multiple images, and return and delivery information</em></figcaption></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>You can turn your pages into rich snippets easily with AIOSEO. </p>\n\n\n\n<h3 class=\"wp-block-heading\" id=\"aioseo-2-choose-keywords-that-are-easy-to-rank-for\">2. Choose Keywords That are Easy to Rank For</h3>\n\n\n\n<p>Quality is the #1 ranking factor. This is where good SEO decisions start.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>One of the best practices for creating content that ranks is to choose a focus keyphrase (keyword) to base your content on. You can think of your target keyword as the <em>main topic</em> of your page.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>The problem is some keywords are nearly impossible to rank for, while others are easy to rank for.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>To create content that ranks, start by <a href=\"https://aioseo.com/keyword-difficulty-in-seo-what-is-it-and-how-to-use-it/\">choosing valuable keywords that are <em>easy to rank for</em></a>.</p>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\" id=\"aioseo-how-to-create-sponsored-links-using-aioseo\">How to Create Sponsored Links Using AIOSEO</h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Perhaps you’re selling advertorials or guest post space on your WordPress site.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>You can use AIOSEO to easily add the sponsored attribute (or other attributes) to links. You can do this right in the WordPress editor.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>To see how it works, navigate to an article in the WordPress editor.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Click on the WordPress chain icon to add a link. Immediately, a pop-up window with toggle buttons opens.</p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"1024\" height=\"634\" src=\"https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/use-aioseo-to-add-sponsored-link-1024x634.png\" alt=\"add sponsored links in wordpress\" class=\"wp-image-244511\" srcset=\"https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/use-aioseo-to-add-sponsored-link-1024x634.png 1024w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/use-aioseo-to-add-sponsored-link-300x186.png 300w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/use-aioseo-to-add-sponsored-link-768x475.png 768w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/use-aioseo-to-add-sponsored-link-1536x951.png 1536w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/use-aioseo-to-add-sponsored-link-600x371.png 600w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/use-aioseo-to-add-sponsored-link-97x60.png 97w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/use-aioseo-to-add-sponsored-link-145x90.png 145w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/use-aioseo-to-add-sponsored-link.png 1806w\" sizes=\"100vw\" /></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>Here you can toggle on sponsored, nofollow, or ugc link attributes.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>You also have the option to toggle on “Open in new tab.” Selecting any of the toggle buttons causes the appropriate code to be added to your links</p>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\" id=\"aioseo-qa-on-sponsored-links\">Q&amp;A on Sponsored Links</h2>\n\n\n\n<div data-schema-only=\"false\" class=\"wp-block-aioseo-faq\" id=\"aioseo-why-not-pay-for-links-and-omit-the-sponsored-tag\"><h3 class=\"aioseo-faq-block-question\">Why not pay for links and omit the sponsored tag?</h3><div class=\"aioseo-faq-block-answer\">\n<p>Many websites that exist for the sole purpose of selling links offer to omit the sponsored tag. However, it’s dangerous to engage in this trade. The reason is that Google can detect and penalize sites involved in such <a href=\"https://developers.google.com/search/docs/essentials/spam-policies\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener nofollow\" title=\"\">link schemes</a>.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Many of these sites offering <a href=\"https://aioseo.com/what-are-paid-links-in-seo/\" title=\"\">paid links</a> without sponsored tags, are “splogs” (spam blogs) or PBNs (private blog networks). These sites have easily recognizable characteristics that Google’s algorithms can detect. In addition, sites paying for links often create guest posts to be published on these sites. And these guest posts may have similarities, which send a red flag to Google as well.</p>\n</div></div>\n\n\n\n<div data-schema-only=\"false\" class=\"wp-block-aioseo-faq\" id=\"aioseo-how-much-does-a-sponsored-link-cost\"><h3 class=\"aioseo-faq-block-question\">How much does a sponsored link cost?</h3><div class=\"aioseo-faq-block-answer\">\n<p>Sponsored links vary in cost and may range from a low of around $20 all the way up to 5 figures. Link sellers often try to extract high prices from sites they perceive to be highly profitable. Prices are often negotiated between the selling and buying parties.</p>\n</div></div>\n\n\n\n<div data-schema-only=\"false\" class=\"wp-block-aioseo-faq\" id=\"aioseo-are-google-ads-considered-sponsored-links\"><h3 class=\"aioseo-faq-block-question\">Are Google Ads considered sponsored links?</h3><div class=\"aioseo-faq-block-answer\">\n<p>Yes, sometimes the links in <a href=\"https://support.google.com/google-ads/answer/1722087?hl=en\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener nofollow\" title=\"\">Google Ads</a> are called sponsored links. Google also offers a type of sponsored link where your website&#8217;s search snippet, instead of a visual ad, is featured at (or near) the top of Google search results. These ads are clearly marked as “Sponsored.”</p>\n\n\n\n<p>As with all Google Ads, your exact display position will depend on Ad Rank, a type of quality score that factors in your landing page experience and expected click-through rate (CTR).</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Google Ads are a type of PPC (pay-per-click) ad. Create a free Google Adwords account to research cost-per-click (CPC) for relevant keywords.</p>\n</div></div>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"1024\" height=\"530\" src=\"https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/plumber-sponsored-ad-links-1024x530.png\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-244572\" srcset=\"https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/plumber-sponsored-ad-links-1024x530.png 1024w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/plumber-sponsored-ad-links-300x155.png 300w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/plumber-sponsored-ad-links-768x398.png 768w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/plumber-sponsored-ad-links-1536x795.png 1536w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/plumber-sponsored-ad-links-600x311.png 600w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/plumber-sponsored-ad-links-116x60.png 116w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/plumber-sponsored-ad-links-174x90.png 174w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/plumber-sponsored-ad-links.png 1820w\" sizes=\"100vw\" /><figcaption class=\"wp-element-caption\"><em>Above: Example of a Google sponsored link that appears for the local search query “plumbers.”</em></figcaption></figure>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\" id=\"aioseo-resources-on-link-building\">Resources on Link Building</h2>\n\n\n\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"https://aioseo.com/seo-guide-nofollow-sponsored-ugc-links/\">An SEO Guide to Nofollow, Sponsored, and UGC Links</a></li>\n\n\n\n<li><a href=\"https://aioseo.com/what-are-paid-links-in-seo/\">What Are Paid Links in SEO and Do They Work?</a></li>\n\n\n\n<li><a href=\"https://aioseo.com/fix-broken-links-in-wordpress/\">How to Find and Fix Broken Links in WordPress</a></li>\n\n\n\n<li><a href=\"https://aioseo.com/referring-domains-vs-backlinks-seo/\">Referring Domains and Backlinks: What’s the Difference (Plus: SEO Impact)</a></li>\n\n\n\n<li><a href=\"https://aioseo.com/how-to-use-link-assistant-to-optimize-your-internal-linking-strategy/\">How to Use Link Assistant to Optimize Your Internal Linking Strategy</a></li>\n\n\n\n<li><a href=\"https://aioseo.com/ways-link-assistant-can-save-you-time-on-internal-and-external-link-building/\">6 Ways Link Assistant Can Save You Time on Internal Link Building</a></li>\n\n\n\n<li><a href=\"https://aioseo.com/link-building-guide/\">The Ultimate Link-Building Guide</a></li>\n\n\n\n<li><a href=\"https://aioseo.com/link-building-statistics/\">29 Link Building Statistics to Power Your SEO Strategy</a></li>\n\n\n\n<li><a href=\"https://aioseo.com/how-to-create-jump-links-in-wordpress/\">How to Create Jump Links in WordPress (and Increase Your Visibility in SERPs)</a></li>\n\n\n\n<li><a href=\"https://aioseo.com/what-are-serps/\">What Are Search Engine Results Pages (SERPs) and Why Are They Important for SEO?</a></li>\n</ul>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\" id=\"aioseo-after-sponsored-links\">After Sponsored Links . .  </h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Now that you’ve learned what sponsored links are, and learned why backlinks are an important part of digital marketing strategy, what’s next?</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Explore the <a href=\"https://aioseo.com/referring-domains-vs-backlinks-seo/\">role of backlinks in revenue</a> or learn more about <a href=\"https://aioseo.com/what-are-paid-links-in-seo/\">paid links</a>.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Join us on our<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/c/AIOSEO\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener nofollow\" title=\"\"> YouTube Channel</a> for easy-to-follow WordPress SEO tutorials. You can also follow us on social media at <a href=\"https://twitter.com/aioseopack\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener nofollow\" title=\"\">X (Twitter)</a>,<a href=\"https://www.linkedin.com/company/aioseo/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener nofollow\" title=\"\"> LinkedIn</a>, or <a href=\"https://facebook.com/aioseopack/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener nofollow\" title=\"\">Facebook</a> to stay in the loop.</p>The post <a href=\"https://aioseo.com/sponsored-links-what-are-they-and-do-they-impact-seo/\">Sponsored Links: What are They and Do They Impact SEO?</a> first appeared on <a href=\"https://aioseo.com\">AIOSEO</a>.\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:36:\"http://wellformedweb.org/CommentAPI/\";a:1:{s:10:\"commentRss\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:77:\"https://aioseo.com/sponsored-links-what-are-they-and-do-they-impact-seo/feed/\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\