eautiful WordPress site in minutes. It’s a very popular drag-and-drop page builder for WordPress and is used on over 1 million sites. The plugin allows you to easily customize your website design and create custom page layouts without writing any code.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Besides being a site and theme builder, SeedProd can also be used as a page builder. You can use this powerful plugin to build high-converting landing pages for your site. These include product pages, email opt-in pages, coming soon pages, maintenance mode pages, and more.</p>\n\n\n\n<p><strong>Pricing</strong>: Starts from $39.50/year.</p>\n\n\n\n<h3 class=\"wp-block-heading\" id=\"aioseo-7-sucuri\">7. <a href=\"https://aioseo.com/recommends/sucuri/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener nofollow\" title=\"Sucuri\">Sucuri</a></h3>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><a href=\"http://aioseo.com/recommends/sucuri/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"702\" height=\"364\" src=\"https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/what-is-a-plugin-sucuri.png\" alt=\"Sucuri homepage\" class=\"wp-image-239506\" srcset=\"https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/what-is-a-plugin-sucuri.png 702w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/what-is-a-plugin-sucuri-300x156.png 300w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/what-is-a-plugin-sucuri-600x311.png 600w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 702px) 100vw, 702px\" /></a></figure>\n\n\n\n<p><a href=\"https://aioseo.com/recommends/sucuri/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener nofollow\" title=\"Sucuri\">Sucuri</a> is a WordPress plugin that offers one of the best WordPress security solutions. Thanks to real-time monitoring and malware scanning, it helps fortify your site against threats and vulnerabilities.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Sucuri also offers a firewall that safeguards your site from DDoS attacks and has powerful features like security hardening and post-hack remediation to ensure your website stays secure.&nbsp;</p>\n\n\n\n<p><strong>Pricing</strong>: Paid plans start at $199.99.</p>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\" id=\"aioseo-what-is-a-plugin-your-faqs-answered\">What is a Plugin? Your FAQs Answered</h2>\n\n\n\n<h3 class=\"wp-block-heading\" id=\"aioseo-what-is-a-wordpress-plugin\">What is a plugin?</h3>\n\n\n\n<p>A WordPress plugin is software that adds specific features or functionality to a WordPress website. It extends the core capabilities of WordPress, allowing users to customize and enhance their websites without extensive coding.</p>\n\n\n\n<h3 class=\"wp-block-heading\" id=\"aioseo-can-i-create-my-own-wordpress-plugin\">Can I create my own WordPress plugin?</h3>\n\n\n\n<p>Yes, if you have coding skills, you can create custom WordPress plugins to add specific functionality to your website. WordPress provides extensive documentation and resources for plugin development.</p>\n\n\n\n<h3 class=\"wp-block-heading\" id=\"aioseo-what-is-the-best-plugin-for-wordpress-seo\">What is the best plugin for WordPress SEO?</h3>\n\n\n\n<p>The best WordPress SEO plugin is All In One SEO (AIOSEO), as it offers a rich feature set to help you rank your site higher on search engine results pages (SERPs).&nbsp;</p>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\" id=\"aioseo-what-is-a-plugin-the-key-to-enhanced-site-functionality\">What is a Plugin? The Key to Enhanced Site Functionality</h2>\n\n\n\n<p>What is a plugin?</p>\n\n\n\n<p>WordPress plugins are a great way to enhance your site’s functionality and features. With plugins, you can transform a simple website into any type of website.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>We hope this post helped you know everything you need to know about WordPress plugins. You may also want to check out other articles on our blog, like our <a href=\"https://aioseo.com/ultimate-wordpress-seo-guide/\" title=\"Ultimate WordPress SEO Guide: Optimize Your Site in 2023\">ultimate WordPress SEO guide</a> or our guide to <a href=\"https://aioseo.com/how-to-get-an-unlimited-free-trial-of-aioseo-lite/\" title=\"Ultimate WordPress SEO Guide: Optimize Your Site in 2023\">getting unlimited access to All In One SEO</a> (SEO).</p>\n\n\n\n<p>If you found this article helpful, then please subscribe to our <a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/c/AIOSEO\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener nofollow\" title=\"\">YouTube Channel</a>. You’ll find many more helpful tutorials there. You can also follow us on <a href=\"https://twitter.com/aioseopack\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener nofollow\" title=\"\">X (Twitter)</a>, <a href=\"https://www.linkedin.com/company/aioseo/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener nofollow\" title=\"\">LinkedIn</a>, or <a href=\"https://facebook.com/aioseopack/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener nofollow\" title=\"\">Facebook</a> to stay in the loop.</p>The post <a href=\"https://aioseo.com/what-is-a-plugin-beginners-guide-to-wordpress-plugins/\">What is a Plugin? The Beginner’s Guide to WordPress Plugins</a> first appeared on <a href=\"https://aioseo.com\">AIOSEO</a>.\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:36:\"http://wellformedweb.org/CommentAPI/\";a:1:{s:10:\"commentRss\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:78:\"https://aioseo.com/what-is-a-plugin-beginners-guide-to-wordpress-plugins/feed/\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:38:\"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/slash/\";a:1:{s:8:\"comments\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:1:\"0\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}}}}}s:27:\"http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom\";a:1:{s:4:\"link\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:0:\"\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:1:{s:0:\"\";a:3:{s:4:\"href\";s:24:\"https://aioseo.com/feed/\";s:3:\"rel\";s:4:\"self\";s:4:\"type\";s:19:\"application/rss+xml\";}}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:44:\"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/syndicatio